CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. 26 reads: "Who Will Be "Miss WILY"? you pick the winner...Mildred Ann Briscoe, Pittsburgh, Announcement of the winner and the coronation of "Miss WILY" will take place at Warners Cinerama, 336 Fifth Ave., Tuesday Evening, November 27th."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Mildred Ann Briscoe wearing boatneck striped dress with brooch, posed in interior with light colored wall for "Miss WILY" contest, another version
